              <T n="single">0x6D7038F7<!--String: "Feeling Festive? Gibbi Point has you covered! You can check out any one of our many unique festivals.\n\nFitness Fest takes place Monday - Wednesday from 9AM - 6PM in Jellyfish Junction. Watch out for Wacky Wednesdays—you'll feel out of place if you're not costumed!\nThe Glow and Flow Festival takes place every New Moon from 7PM - 2AM in Jellyfish Junction. Be sure to try out a special swim!\nThe Sunrise, Sunset Festival takes place on weekends from 1PM - 6PM in the Crystal Valley neighborhood. This is the best way to catch a super-special butterfly.\nThe 'Round the Fire Festival takes place on weekends from 7PM - 2AM in the Wanderwood Wilds neighborhoods. Come by for some storytelling!"--></T>
